what_failed: Regression (0.92x): Isolated three dimension tables (date_dim, customer_address, web_site) into separate CTEs with their respective filters before joining with the main web_sales table. This enables early predicate pushdown and creates small hash tables for efficient probing. Preserved original EXISTS/NOT EXISTS subqueries as-is to maintain short-circuit evaluation semantics.
why_it_failed: Materialized a GROUP BY self-join (HAVING MIN() <> MAX()) on the entire fact table BEFORE applying date/address/call_center filters. The original query filters catalog_sales first via correlated EXISTS clauses, then checks warehouse conditions. Pre-materializing the unfiltered self-join creates a massive intermediate result the optimizer cannot cost-estimate correctly.
